name: Osiris Alliance Ship and LPC Blueprint Package
desc: A complete set of blueprints from the Osiris Alliance R&D department. Enables heavy industry to construct the hulls and fighter LPCs specified in the package.

name: Osiris Alliance Weapon Blueprint Package
desc: A complete set of weapon blueprints from the Osiris Alliance R&D department. Contains top secret designs that are in current service. Enables heavy industry to construct the weapons

name: Top Secret Osiris Alliance Blueprint Package
desc: A complete set of the 3rd generation blueprints from the Osiris Alliance R&D department. A closely guarded secret, one can but wonder how these can be found as a neat package. Any core system would gladly get their hands on the ORB technology. Enables heavy industry to construct the hulls, weapons and fighter LPCs specified in the package.

name: Power Jinx R&D Blueprint Package
desc: A set of blueprints and hacks from Power Jinx R&D. The blueprints contain mostly civilian ships merged with military systems. Enables heavy industry to construct the hulls, weapons and fighter LPCs specified in the package.

name: Antimatter Energy Group Blueprint Package
desc: A collection of hacks and after-market modification specs that enables heavy industry to construct the hulls used by the Antimatter Energy Group.
